Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.34,0:00:18.31,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:29.77,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:36.71,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:47.83,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:56.77,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:01:08.66,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:20.54,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:26.38,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:36.18,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:29.77,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:36.71,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:47.83,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:56.77,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:01:08.66,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:20.54,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:26.38,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:36.18,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.06,0:01:49.96,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(290,390)}Ep. 46 - The Wombat in the Pit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:02:01.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Together with dad, we went to see the mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:18.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That was where we found the wallabies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:21.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should take it with us\Nand bring it up at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:23.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:29.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob chased after the baby wallaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:34.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As cute as it is, bringing it up\Nfrom such a small age is probably impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:35.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:38.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go any further, Tob!\NCome back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.64,0:02:43.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:51.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob! Tob! Tob!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.28,0:02:54.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:55.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.41,0:02:57.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob suddenly disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:58.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:03.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob! Tob, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:04.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:07.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, you were watching him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:09.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}was{\i0} watching, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:13.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If so, you were supposed to notice,\Nexactly where Tob disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:15.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's was exactly around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:19.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You've only seen it from afar,\Nso maybe we should walk a little further?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:21.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob! Are you hiding somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:23.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:26.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate? Kate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:34.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Here! I'm here! Tob is here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:43.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate! Is it this pit?\NDid you fall into this pit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:45.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see you from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:48.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I can see you from here!\NIt's because it's so dark in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.89,0:03:51.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So you two aren't hurt, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:53.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:54.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:58.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:00.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop crying, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:01.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:04.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My butt kinda hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:05.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can you get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:06.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:08.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going out first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:12.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you respond\Nwhen we called out to you from above?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:14.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I probably fainted.\NThat must be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:15.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:18.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I came to my senses when you landed on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:19.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it doesn't hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.93,0:04:22.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A little, in my shoulder.\NBut I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:25.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you try to climb out first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:27.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come out sooner, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:29.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob is coming right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:35.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:41.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, put your feet on my shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:43.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll soil your dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:46.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now's not the time to be saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:48.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, then...
Comment: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:49.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:58.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Climb a little higher!\NI'll pull you up from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:07.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Useless. I can't climb here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:08.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Head, head!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:09.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:11.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Stand on my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:13.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.03,0:05:14.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, hurry up!
Comment: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:15.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:05:18.23,0:05:19.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:21.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little more, Tob!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:24.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:27.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A bit more!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:41.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Here, give me your hand, Tob.\NYou're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:43.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Here, take my hand!
Comment: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:44.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:49.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:52.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:55.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You almost did it.\NLet's give it another try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:59.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's pointless. I can't climb that, sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.03,0:06:01.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Stop saying that and try once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:03.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob! Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:07.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, I'll push you up with my head again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:36.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The rent is cheap,\Nso we gotta make do with this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:39.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But living here for five years would be too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:41.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Clara and Ben won't be living with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.75,0:06:45.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,and if it's just us and three little children,\Nthis company housing should suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:47.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Children grow up fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:53.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you're saying\Nyou don't want to live in this company housing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:55.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What I said was not just about the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:59.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It was about this whole "working in a mine" affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:01.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, there are no schools around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:03.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You could teach them yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.32,0:07:08.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, honey, do you really feel\Nthat working here is your best option?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:10.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I never said it's the {\i1}best{\i0} option.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:13.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought things through\Nbefore opting out for this work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:15.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you think about it for a little more?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:18.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No other job around here pays quite as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:19.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Still, if I could get you to rethink...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:23.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. I think I'll go back\Nto where we left the children now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.62,0:07:24.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:28.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting there until you finish\Nyour business in the office! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:30.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. It won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:35.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob! Left! Your left!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:38.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob, there's a protrusion just above your left foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:40.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Try to put your foot on that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:43.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not your right! Left! Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:47.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Left, I said! Geez!\NCan't you tell right from left?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:49.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:52.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, just a little more!\NGrab my hand, Tob.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:55.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, other! Give me your other hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:56.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:01.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob! Your foot to the right! Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.24,0:08:06.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Good! Don't let your guard down. Slowly. Slowly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy, start pulling yourself back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:11.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But don't rush! Do it slower!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:14.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good! One last push, keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:31.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you crying about now, Tob?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:33.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Kate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:36.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Try to climb up, Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:41.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid. There's no way I can climb out myself.\NThat's why I let Tob get out first. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:43.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What would we do, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:45.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:49.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I could get out if we had a rope or a ladder.\NIn other words, go find an adult first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. I'll go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:53.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Make it quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:53.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:56.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go bring some adult here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:58.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:02.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You want to leave Kate all alone in this pit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:07.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, if you see someone passing through here,\Nask for their help, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:08.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:10.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be on my way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:10.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:20.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:22.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:25.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:26.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:28.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:33.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone owes me an apology, that's gotta be\Nthe guy who dug this pit out then left it as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:38.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This pit was certainly dug out by people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:03.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Could there be something in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:06.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:08.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Oh, shucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:18.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tob! Tob, is Lucy not back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.49,0:10:21.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't she just barely left?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:24.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get out soon!\NThere's something in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:25.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:28.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There's something in this tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:47.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad! Dad, it's serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:49.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:51.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's very serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:11.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:12.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:14.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:15.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, rope! The rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:17.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:27.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, what's in there?\NA snake? A lizard?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:29.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see it, I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:31.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine, just hang in there!
Comment: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:51.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's Kate's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.72,0:11:53.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.16,0:12:11.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just a wombat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:41.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like someone didn't bother\Nto properly bar his trial mine... 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:42.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:47.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really shriek that terribly\Nfrom seeing an animal so peaceful?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:49.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't sound like yourself. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:52.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How may times do I have to tell you?\NI couldn't see well there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:56.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, this wombat is still a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:03.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Spare for Lucy, who felt elated\Non the occasion of finding a wombat she could keep,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:07.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,on our way back from the mine,\Neveryone was in pretty low spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, they returned so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:52.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That was really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:02.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome ba...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:09.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:13.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon. I'm Mr. Princeton's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:16.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! So, the one who helped Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.84,0:14:19.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And you must be... Ms. Clara, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:24.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.\NYou've done so much for my little sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:26.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, please, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:29.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where's everyone today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:34.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, father would likely\Nsoon start working in a mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:38.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,so he went to look at the mine and the company lodgings\Ntogether with my mother and siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:43.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I was just preparing a portion of tea.\NWould you like some? 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:44.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:50.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So, Lucy also went there with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:51.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:53.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Which mine did they go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:57.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm not mistaken, it's the one near Mount Barker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:15:00.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, could it be our company's mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:01.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:06.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty sure my husband told me\Nhe invested into a mine near Mount Barker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:08.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:14.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the company my dad\Nwould be working for is Mr. Princeton's company?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:15.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:19.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What a coincidence!\NI'm sure dad had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.34,0:15:21.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just saying he invested in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:26.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My husband is not exactly the head of that company,\Nso I can't know for sure. 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:31.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is?\NTurns out, it was Mr. Princeton's company? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:35.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad went to Mr. Princeton's company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:37.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:47.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So, at what hour do you expect everyone to be back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:51.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't exactly predict\Nhow much time it would take them...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:52.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:53.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:16:01.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it from Lucy.\NYou're engaged, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:03.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My, Lucy talking too much again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:05.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So it's true, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:06.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.01,0:16:08.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you getting married soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:12.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When you do, be sure to invite me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:13.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:15.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're Lucy's big sister, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:19.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So I really feel like you're a daughter\Nof some relative of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:24.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When do you think it'll be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:27.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the wedding ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:29.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:31.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, when will Lucy return?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:52.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that mine\Nbelongs to Mr. Princeton's company.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:57.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Mrs. Princeton told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:17:00.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Life is full of interesting coincidences.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:04.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's more interesting, that Mr. Princeton\Nseems to be awfully rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:07.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Clara, what did Mrs. Princeton come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:10.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't quite understand it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:13.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But above all, I believe, she wanted to see Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:15.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just for that? 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:17.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seemed so to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:23.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If it hadn't been so, why'd she ask me to pass to Lucy\Nthat she absolutely wants Lucy to come visit her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:25.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. Ah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:31.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next Sunday, can take Lucy\Nfor a visit to the Princetons house?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:35.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm morbidly curious\Nto look at the mansion they're living in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:37.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:38.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:41.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take Lucy there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:46.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it,\Nwhen Mr. Princeton came the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:49.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He said he wanted to have a talk\Nwith you about farming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:51.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:56.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, to think that the mine we've been to\Nbelongs to Mr. Princeton too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:08.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen Little. You can by no means bully this baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:18.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If he was still a wild dingo,\Nhe'd totally attack a wombat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:20.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,With Little, it'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:23.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose. He never attacked the sheep, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:29.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, how about I make a nest for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:31.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:33.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't give it a name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:34.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:44.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You sure have a funny little face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:47.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.68,0:18:49.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.49,0:18:51.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:53.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, you've a very red face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:56.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My head hurts too. For a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:01.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You've a fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:13.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Going already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:14.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.98,0:19:18.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to go too!\NTo see the Princeton Mansion and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:21.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not while you're ill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:25.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've not been ill even once\Never since we came to Southern Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:28.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the last time I'm going to Princetons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:32.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm yet to go there time and again after this.\NThat's what I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:35.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Their Missus smelled really nice, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:37.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's because she uses a perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:41.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:42.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:20:00.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The next day, with Lucy in tow,\Ndad went to visit to the Princetons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:34.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quite impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:35.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.80,0:20:38.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time\NI'm entering a mansion so gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:47.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you could make it, Mr. Popple.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.57,0:20:49.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for inviting us. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:53.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy! I'm so glad to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:03.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Popple, my husband is currently out,\Nbut he'll be back before long.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:05.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You could wait for him over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:06.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Prospero!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.30,0:21:09.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You still remember me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:13.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.15,0:21:24.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You've a beautiful garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.19,0:21:26.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've not been able to look after it very well lately. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:28.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't it really curious?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:32.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Back when Lucy lived here,\Nshe used to go play a lot in this garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:36.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And I think that was what made the garden\Ntruly bright and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:39.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy is incredibly fond of animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:44.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When she played with birds in this garden,\Nnot yet having recovered her memory,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.73,0:21:48.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,and said to me,\N"I seems, I was a very animal-loving girl,"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.59,0:21:50.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I was deeply moved by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:52.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:55.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Seems like my husband is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.86,0:21:59.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:04.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I came to see you just as you requested. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:09.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say if we leave the ladies here\Nand proceed to over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.04,0:22:11.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to talk to you in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.28,0:22:11.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.41,0:22:20.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.49,0:22:24.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get straight to it, Mr. Popple.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.78,0:22:27.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't work at a mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.89,0:22:28.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.58,0:22:32.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If it's fine with you,\NI'd like you to work at my farm instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:34.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:36.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't ask you to give your answer right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.97,0:22:41.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, if you'd say you want to work at a mine\Nno matter what, that's fine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:46.44,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,However, Mr. Popple, didn't you come to this country\Nin order to work in agriculture?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.44,0:22:47.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:54.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, first of all, I wanted to listen\Nto your thoughts about agriculture today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:09.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Lucy.\NDo you like this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.01,0:23:11.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's pretty and big.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:16.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I'd be the happiest ever\Nif you stayed in this house from now on and forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.58,0:23:53.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I so wanted to go to the Princeton Mansion...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.00,0:23:58.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy is probably having lots of fun by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.38,0:24:06.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Our wombat Funny ran away into the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.41,0:24:10.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just as Mr. Pettywell's carriage was driving by.\NWatch out, Funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.09,0:24:13.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Lucy-May of the Southern Rainbow:\N"Dad's Decision".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.73,0:24:15.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
